high_descs: Turn right and face the sink.
Pick up the apple next to the drain.
Turn around and face microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave and place the apple on the plate to the right of the egg. Turn on the microwave for a few seconds, then open the door and remove the heated apple. Close the door.
Turn left and head to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the apple on the middle shelf to the right of the lettuce. Close the refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple next to the lettuce on the middle shelf in the refrigerator.

high_descs: turn right to the sink
grab the apple from the sink
turn around to the microwave
open the microwave, put the apple in, heat the apple for a while, take the apple out
turn around, walk to the refrigerator on the right
open the refrigerator, put the apple in
anns.task_desc: cook the apple in the microwave, put the apple in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn right to face sink.
Pick up green apple from sink, located to the right of the spoon.
Turn around to face stove and microwave.
Open microwave door, place apple on the right side of the microwave opposite the egg, shut the microwave door.  Open microwave door after five seconds.
Remove apple from microwave, close door.  Turn left, move to fridge.  Turn right to face fridge.
Open fridge door, place apple to the right of lettuce, close fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Cook apple and place in fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and face the sink.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Turn around and walk a step right to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Place the apple in the fridge to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to face the silver sink.
Pick up the green apple inside the sink next to the spoon.
Turn left and head towards the silver stove on your left.
Look above the stove, open the microwave door, place the apple inside next to the egg, close the door, heat it for a moment, open the door, pick up the apple and close the microwave door.
Turn around, go towards the counter with the sink, turn right to cross the room to face the white fridge on your right.
Open the fridge door, place the apple on the middle shelf to the right of the lettuce and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Turn left, walk forward, then turn left at the stove.
Place the apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the apple in the refrigerator.
